    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and the M-Variable limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. This example has undergone extensive mechanical sorting, including reinforced rear subframe mounting points and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul to ensure timing precision. The suspension geometry is preserved with refreshed bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers, providing the signature communicative chassis feedback these cars are known for. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the engine maintains excellent compression and the throttle response remains razor-sharp.",
      "price": 34500.0,
