      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously cared-for 2019 Volvo XC90 T6 Momentum, presented in a striking Crystal White Pearl. This vehicle has been my reliable daily driver and has been maintained with an open checkbook. The exterior paint retains a deep gloss, with only minor road peppering on the front fascia consistent with regular use. Inside, the Charcoal leather interior remains supple and clean, free of any tears or unpleasant odors. Every electronic feature, from the responsive 9-inch Sensus touchscreen to the panoramic moonroof, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is sound; it recently underwent a full multi-point inspection and received a fresh synthetic oil change. The tires are Pirelli All-Seasons with plenty of life remaining. It comes with a complete set of service records and two key fobs. This SUV strikes the perfect balance for someone seeking luxury and safety without the new-car price tag.",
